						<div>
						<p>Hello Terrible Posture Games Community!</p>

						<p dir="ltr">Put the kettle on and pull up your favorite armchair, because&nbsp;YOU ASKED. WE LISTENED. You said &ldquo;Everything is Cozy-this, cozy-that these days!&rdquo; and, at least one of you said, &ldquo;Where is my Cozy Mothergunship: Forge?&rdquo;</p>

						<p dir="ltr">Well, HERE it is, folks! Check out new update trailer on our store pages:<b> </b></p>

						<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://terribleposture.sendybay.com/l/f892x4Mux6oIJcoiKbCo892I2A/xKMSpSreN6OFPyyZ3biCwA/8i0eUOFQR92MYKYPNJbyRg"><img alt="" src="https://www.terribleposture.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/meta_quest_logo.png" style="width: 163px; height: 60px;" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://terribleposture.sendybay.com/l/f892x4Mux6oIJcoiKbCo892I2A/i3OiqBE0pO1MP3z52MyYPg/8i0eUOFQR92MYKYPNJbyRg"><img alt="" src="https://www.terribleposture.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/steam.png" style="width: 163px; height: 60px;" /></a></p>

						<p><em><strong>MOTHERGUNSHIP: FORGE</strong></em>, the acclaimed VR exclusive game already chock full of wacky crafting and wackier action, is seeing its first major update with THE COZY UPDATE, coming out August 18th.</p>
						</div>

						<p data-block-id="block-e52fba4f-4027-43fa-a7b9-6265187a877d"><img alt="" src="https://www.terribleposture.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/MGSVR_COZY_BannerThumbnail-scaled.jpg" style="width: 100%; height: 100%;" /></p>

						<p dir="ltr">What makes a game cozy? Here&rsquo;s all the goodies dropping with the update:</p>

						<ul>
							<li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
							<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">A suite of 20 new Cozy Gunparts, including cute metal cat heads, comfy pillows (also made of metal), yummy metal bento lunches, cozy gift wrapped presents, cups of chamomile, flamethrowers, and more. Players asked, the devs listened; you can now strap a literal cup of tea to your unfathomably large weapon.&nbsp;</p>
							</li>
							<li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
							<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">New HEART Level Set and Boss: only the most emotionally swollen and treacherously spikey rooms ever for THIS update!</p>
							</li>
							<li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
							<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">New Friends! (Enemies. They aren&rsquo;t friendly at all).&nbsp;</p>
							</li>
							<li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
							<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">SANDBOX MODE: As requested by fans, Sandbox Mode allows players to explore the Mothergunship with the full array of their collection at their disposal.</p>
							</li>
							<li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
							<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">ENDLESS MODE: The fun never ends in this mode. What&rsquo;s more cozy than that?&nbsp;</p>
							</li>
							<li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
							<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">AND, FOR THE ADVENTUROUS: Terrible Posture Games invites players to participate in the new BETA CO-OP CAMPAIGN! Find a friend and fight through the entirety of Mothergunship&rsquo;s campaign together!</p>
							</li>
							<li aria-level="1" dir="ltr">
							<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">And, of course, tons more: weapon favoriting, new ways to explore your run history, tons of (cozy) bug fixes, quality of life improvements, and design adjustments.</p>
							</li>
						</ul>

						<p>Interested in meeting other fans, talking about Terrible Posture Games&#39; projects and getting the scoop on news and announcements? Then join us at our discord at <a data-link-card="true" href="https://terribleposture.sendybay.com/l/f892x4Mux6oIJcoiKbCo892I2A/7aK9B8928i763dM892O6Zd1DYfLQ/8i0eUOFQR92MYKYPNJbyRg" target="_blank">discord.terribleposture.com</a>!</p>
